title: Rosebud Baker, Brian Austin Green, Jake Paul V Conor McGregor, and We Were Right About Doming
description:
Subscribe, Rate, and Leave a review! -The US Goverment considered Doming to fight coronavirus -Jake Paul is going to taunt Conor McGregor into a fight -AITA Thursday -Voicemails Rosebud Baker returns to the show.
